choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Sure, here's a healthy meal plan for you today:
Breakfast: Greek yogurt with berries and granola
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, tomatoes, cucumbers, and balsamic vinaigrette dressing
Snack: Apple slices with almond butter
Dinner: Baked tilapia with roasted vegetables (such as broccoli, carrots, and bell peppers) and quinoa
Remember to drink plenty of water throughout the day!
